<p><span style="border-bottom: 12px solid #dcf1fb; padding: 0 0 0 0.2em;">2_1_훈련 세트와 테스트 세트</span></p>

<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>정의</title>
